f1: MATRIX   with ALL Degrees of Freedom (DoF) of Velocity X + Velocity Y + Pressure.
f2: MATRICES with doF of 1 component of Velocity or Pressure. Fractional step Method.
cr: Direct    Method by Crout    factorization AG=L D Lt with ALL DoF
ch: Direct    Method by Cholesky factorization AG=L Lt   with DoF of 1 component of Velocity or Pressure
cg: Iterative Method by Simple Conjugate Gradient        with DoF of 1 component of Velocity or Pressure

VEXNORM(Node) = SQRT(  XExactVelocity**2 + YExactVelocity**2 + ZExactVelocity**2 )
VERROR (Node) = SQRT( (XExactVelocity-XComputedVelocity)**2 
                    + (YExactVelocity-YComputedVelocity)**2
                    + (ZExactVelocity-ZComputedVelocity)**2 )
VEXASOM = Sum( VEXNORM(Node) )
VEXAMX  = MAX( VEXNORM(Node) )
VERRSOM = Sum( VERROR(Node) )
VERRMX  = MAX( VERROR(Node) )
VERRLMX = MAX( VERROR(Node) / VEXNORM(Node) )

VERRMX              = MAX  ABS VELOCITY ERROR = MXAVE
VERRMX/VEXAMX*100   = MAX  REL VELOCITY ERROR = MXRVE
VERRLMX             = NODE REL VELOCITY ERROR = MNRVE
VERRSOM/VEXASOM*100 = MEAN REL VELOCITY ERROR = MERVE

